respondents-informed-consent: Bonke abaphendulile emkhankasweni banikeze imvume enolwazi.
pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Idatha eboniswe kule deshibhodi iqoqwa ngokuqondile ezimpendulweni zenhlolovo futhi ayiveli kwizibalo zezwe ezisemthethweni noma amasethi edatha. Imele imibono evezwe abantu abasha ngesikhathi socwaningo, futhi noma yiziphi iziphetho ezitholwa kulezi zimpendulo ziwumsebenzi womsebenzisi, hhayi i-PMNCH. I-PMNCH izibophezele ekuhlonipheni, ekuthuthukiseni nasekuvikeleni amalungelo kanye nenhlalakahle yabo bonke abantu. Noma imiphi imibono evezwe ezimpendulweni zenhlolovo noma izinto ezishicilelwe eziphuma kule deshibhodi ezingqubuzana nalokhu kuzibophezela akugunyazwa yi-PMNCH.

click-bubble-country-information: Chofoza inganekwane ukuze uguqule amabhamuza, chofoza amabhamuza ukuze ubuke ulwazi lwezwe.
wra03a-click-view-topic-responses: Chofoza esihlokweni ukuze ubuke izimpendulo. Abanye besifazane bakhulume ngezihloko ezingaphezu kwesisodwa. Hambisa phezulu kwebha ukuze ubone izinombolo negama lesigaba.

to-protect-anonymity: Ukuze kuvikelwe ukungaziwa, abanye abaphendulayo basusiwe kule deshibhodi.
wra03a-subtext: Thola ukufinyelela ezimpendulweni ezivulekile eziyizigidi ezingu-1.2 ngale deshibhodi esebenzisanayo, ithuluzi eliyingqayizivele elixhumanisa amazwi abesifazane namantombazane kanye namathuba angapheli okuhlaziywa kwedijithali.
pmn01a-subtext: Siyakwamukela Kudeshibhodi ethi “Lokho Intsha Eyifunayo”! Leli thuluzi elisebenzisanayo linikeza ukumelwa okubonakalayo kwezimpendulo kanye nemininingwane esiyiqoqayo kubantu abasha abaneminyaka engu-10-24 emhlabeni jikelele. Umnyombo wesinyathelo ngumbuzo ovulekile: "Ukuze ngithuthukise inhlalakahle yami, ngifuna ...". Abantu abasha abavela kuwo wonke umhlaba bebephendula lokhu, besinika ukuqonda okuyingqayizivele ngezidingo zabo, amathemba, kanye nezifiso zabo. Hlola idatha, thola izindaba ezingemuva kwezinombolo, futhi uhlanganyele nathi ekwandiseni amazwi abantu abasha abayizigidi eziyizinkulungwane eziyi-1.8 emhlabeni jikelele. Ukuze ufunde kabanzi mayelana nomkhankaso, vakashela ku-http://www.1point8.org.
midwife-subtext: Sabuza ababelethisi emhlabeni wonke lo mbuzo: “Yini oyifunayo kakhulu endimeni yakho yokuba umbelethisi?”
giz-subtext: Sabuza abesifazane abangu-10603 eMexico lo mbuzo, “¿Qué es lo que más deseas o necesitas para encontrar empleo o un mejor empleo? Sicela, comparte sólo la petición más importante para ti.“, (Yini oyifuna kakhulu noma oyidingayo ukuze uthole umsebenzi noma umsebenzi ongcono? Sicela wabelane ngesicelo esibaluleke kakhulu kuwe kuphela.)
healthwellbeing-title: Lokho abesifazane abakufunayo ngempilo nokuphila kahle
healthwellbeing-subtext: Sibuze abesifazane emhlabeni wonke, ukuthi yini abafuna ukuthuthukisa impilo yabo nokuphila kahle.
wwwpakistan-subtext: Sibuze abesifazane abangu-245311 ePakistan, ukuthi bafunani ukuthuthukisa impilo yabo nokuphila kahle.
giz-q1: Yini oyifuna kakhulu noma oyidingayo ukuze uthole umsebenzi noma umsebenzi ongcono? Sicela wabelane ngesicelo esibaluleke kakhulu kuwe kuphela.
giz-q2: Yini okufanele uhulumeni ayenze ukuze akusize uthole umsebenzi oyiphupho lakho? Sicela wabelane ngesicelo esibaluleke kakhulu kuwe kuphela.
